{"tid":429203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］究竟我隻手上面嗰啲係咩來","createTime":"2017-10-08T16:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T16:51:58.000Z","uid":66018,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"601659b3855185285ea07b3fa004faf333586511","tid":429203,"uid":66018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"我係做飲食嘅 做嘢嗰時成日會有油彈上對手度 之後放工返屋企就會見到起咗呢啲粒粒 好痕r完之後個area仲會發熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但第二日就會冇咗 請問有冇皮膚科神醫可以知道佢係咩來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">密集恐懼症患者請迴避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/002746_13229266cbe69cb0ba667ff22819173b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F002746_13229266cbe69cb0ba667ff22819173b.jpg&h=226f65bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/002747_13229266cbe69cb0ba667ff22819173b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F002747_13229266cbe69cb0ba667ff22819173b.jpg&h=ca78f51d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc86f10d520745fa637fb6b64092886013022be","tid":429203,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"Check 下個肝"},{"pid":"52548ef32fc4046248ef8e6b142e9c71bd792765","tid":429203,"uid":67201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17290538dc092101869a62bc1c2af2315e11ec04","tid":429203,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"主婦手"},{"pid":"0c51b49d56b4f1121ad18eaa8212d32a9ae7ee4d","tid":429203,"uid":8343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"睇醫生好啲喎"},{"pid":"ba0e233c955553b591504cc61819b259151b43f9","tid":429203,"uid":82540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"有d 似濕疹"},{"pid":"3c7ed8914fa2d3c52515fb96e3ab06faa16f14ae","tid":429203,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1be63465deae3d7a3a3609c22f2925d3a2f633c5","tid":429203,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d 似濕疹</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49926b2d9ba2f3fef5dac2ba12fc05fb01a3472c","tid":429203,"uid":13121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"好似敏感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39eb585644b85d187164e9c0ea5593be59ba97d","tid":429203,"uid":14130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"風爛，睇醫生啦屌"},{"pid":"8f446baf76cc2f975d56678d84161e993b65b353","tid":429203,"uid":66018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾油彈到先會起？</blockquote><br />\n係呀 但我本身都有濕疹"},{"pid":"92f40769730722776ab40d31ed986c9bcc9f0cb8","tid":429203,"uid":25003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風爛，睇醫生啦屌</blockquote><br />\n我有個同學咪係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後成面同手都係"},{"pid":"33efaa080a4a5876bfefa42afcd1347280f51a30","tid":429203,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"食下治敏速"},{"pid":"779fc9c2db59ba7941a79ed923f6c5f136463ef5","tid":429203,"uid":66018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Check 下個肝</blockquote><br />\n巴打點解咁講？"},{"pid":"1690cfbf8e357163131d5729da56cc880b5be4ee","tid":429203,"uid":28258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"油脂粒定係過敏<br />\n建議睇睇醫生"},{"pid":"7829ef60422e33d600761d3c4d7628d8a23923b6","tid":429203,"uid":66018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d 似濕疹</blockquote><br />\n我係本身有濕疹呀 但淨係會一撻撻咁 唔會好似而家咁一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2789766914004185495c0824507c56a01cd1f46b","tid":429203,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"敏感呀，你做野個度污糟"},{"pid":"9f1d19d39d4289dc94af1b17a40f8032d2e2a366","tid":429203,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風爛，睇醫生啦屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻應該唔係，因為我2種都生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通敏感啫，睇醫生食個藥3 4日左右就好返，但唔睇r爛左會出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733e6905734555dad65e6a8ec46dbcbc7976e9ef","tid":429203,"uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前做過侍應，初初返工時個托盤成日會掂到手腕內側，可能因為托盤底好污糟，之後就生左好多小水胞(同樓主果啲一樣)，好痕，越抓會越擴散。<br />\n之後我多啲洗手，就冇再生，可能身體習慣左掂污糟嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}